{"tid":1649167,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開] 和理非行動討論平台 -- 搞手們入一入","createTime":"2019-10-12T14:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T17:27:10.000Z","uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dde4447b8c1256c505fddbb4441300fc6208c794","tid":1649167,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"依家和理非既行動有以下既問題：<br />\n1) 行動太多，太亂<br />\n同一日可以有唔同既行動，有啲撞時間，有啲就唔知有咩用，有啲就地點差太遠，太散，有時會成版都係行動post，基本上聚唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聚唔到人首先會俾外國人覺得個運動已經停止左，另外一次少人可能會令到下一次更加少人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2) 文宣嚴重不足<br />\n有好多行動都係2日前，甚至即日係連登出post。有好多人包括我基本上唔知道有，有幾次都係啱啱行過即刻join<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位搞手巴絲要知道其實好多人係冇睇連登，初期有好多行動都係靠連儂痴文宣/airdrop 去spread開。如果要搞既話，起碼文宣都要預返最少2日左右，方便聚人<br />\n<br />\n以上兩個問題都可能係因為依家係冇一個平台去俾搞手們去夾時間，大家靠睇連登post入面討論又會好散，所以我開左一個TG group 同TG channel：<br />\n<br />\n和理非行動整合channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/woleifeiaction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwoleifeiaction&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9vZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=31dc5ce4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/woleifeiaction</a><br />\n<br />\n主要功能：<br />\n1) 發佈搞手們係group入面討論完既行動<br />\n2) 如果撞日子又夾唔到既時候，希望可以做埋投票既功能。盡可能將和理非既力量聚埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n和理非行動搞手討論group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/woleifeidiscuss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwoleifeidiscuss&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9vZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=d00acbfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/woleifeidiscuss</a><br />\n<br />\n主要功能：<br />\n1) 俾搞手們去傾/討論黎緊既行動<br />\n2) 希望有埋文宣手足可以加入傾文宣設計<br />\n3) 希望如果係大型(全港性)既可以直接同18區TG 組協調<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望做到個流程係：<br />\nTG group 搞手們傾/夾完 &gt; TG channel發佈 &gt; 連登/連儂/airdrop/落街推文宣<br />\n<br />\n依個平台唔包括任何裝修裝飾快閃行動，因為狗仔一定會入黎mon post。所以以上既行動都係靠各位裝修師傅私下交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原諒樓主一把年紀唔太識用TG，如果巴絲覺得有咩可以改善既就提出，暫時可以試下用依個模式run ，有返個協同效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f75cba1f38f10e78546775a3ce79a2afa92cc4","tid":1649167,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:19:28.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35b44514326da27f2bb506593e6d83bb8885fac4","tid":1649167,"uid":82253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"就快定到日期架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n榮光盃 以波會友 撐morey<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646298</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/StandWithMoreypeanut\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStandWithMoreypeanut&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9vZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=5bc144fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/StandWithMoreypeanut</a>"},{"pid":"f416bf42fa030ed185a69be11bd6403eb5c81d3e","tid":1649167,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b44514326da27f2bb506593e6d83bb8885fac4","tid":1649167,"uid":82253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"就快定到日期架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n榮光盃 以波會友 撐morey<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646298</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/StandWithMoreypeanut\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStandWithMoreypeanut&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9vZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=5bc144fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/StandWithMoreypeanut</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"group入面有位文宣巴絲可以幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /